data.description: This 5 BEDROOM 3 BATHROOM home features a SALTWATER POOL and an OFFICE/HOBBY room. Located in the charming Bronson Ridge subdivision, this home boasts a spacious floor plan that is perfect for entertaining, both inside and out. Parallel to the entryway is a convenient office space with built in floor to ceiling bookshelves. The open kitchen / living room / dining room area is the perfect space for all of your gatherings with family and friends with durable, easy to clean LVT flooring. The kitchen includes the refrigerator and features a gas stove, built-in microwave, and a pantry with island seating for informal dining. Opposite the kitchen, you'll find a full guest bathroom connecting to a bedroom, hallway storage, and a built-in hall tree with bench leading to the 2 car garage. On the upper level is the owner's bedroom plus 3 additional bedrooms. The owner's suite features tray ceilings, 2 walk in closets one with a custom Closet Pro system. The owner's bathroom has a toilet closet, garden tub with subway tile tub surround, and step-in shower with shower seat, subway tile, and glass doors. There are 3 additional bedrooms, 2 with walk-in closets, and a full bathroom. Situated in the center of the upper level, is a laundry room WITH SINK. The recently built (2020) saltwater pool with dive rock will make your home the go-to spot for those hot Summer days. A privacy fence surrounds the backyard oasis with plenty of room for outdoor seating and recreation. The covered patio area is perfect for grilling or finding refuge in the shade. NOTE: all wallpaper and decals are easy to remove peel and stick designs. NO CITY TAXES, PRIME LOCATION, and HIGHLY DESIRABLE SCHOOLS, don't hesitate a smidge and head on over to 108 Bronson Ridge!!
